parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: making it difficult to turn the wheel
especially at low speeds; the steering wheel becomes stiff or hard to turn; the vehicle drifts or pulls to one side; and there may be a hissing or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine cradle/subframe due to rust can cause the sway bar to break away, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: causing the sway bar to break away; the vehicle becomes difficult to steer; and there may be a sudden loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, jerk, or slip, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent transmission problems can cause the vehicle to lose power, jerk, or slip, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates or slips intermittently
the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission sensors can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission makes a grinding or clunking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Throttle Body and Air Intake Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body and air intake can cause the vehicle to surge or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or accelerates unexpectedly
the vehicle makes a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The paint defect on the hood can lead to bubbling, peeling, and corrosion, which can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle and affect its appearance.
symptoms: especially near the front grille and windshield.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The power loss and unintended acceleration can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
The water leak can cause damage to the interior, electrical components, and compromise the safety of the vehicle.
The lift gate failure can cause injury or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: sudden slamming of the lift gate
difficulty opening or closing the lift gate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hood release lever design flaw can cause accidental opening of the hood while driving, which can compromise the safety of the vehicle and its occupants.
symptoms: Accidental opening of the hood while applying the parking brake.
